Class BST<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
  BST<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBST<T>
public class BST<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBST<T>

Class of a binary Search Tree. This class contains methods for finding a record data, finding the maximum and average heights of the binary tree, and displaying the data in the tree. Copyright(C) 2011 Duncan A. Buell. All rights reserved.
